dropdown.name: getCarrierList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from carrier_lku order by description asc

dropdown.name: getLobList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from lob_lku order by description asc

dropdown.name: getCarrierListForDesc
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from carrier_lku order by description asc

dropdown.name: getBusinessSegmentList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select carrier_group_desc,carrier_group_id from carrier_group_lku

dropdown.name: getProducerTypeList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from (select 1 sortOrder, * from producertype_lku where description != 'Other' union all select 2 sortOrder, * from producertype_lku where description = 'Other')x order by sortOrder,description

dropdown.name: getFacilityList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select business_segment_code, business_segment_name from business_segment where (business_segment_type = 1) And (is_active=1) order by business_segment_name asc

dropdown.name: getAppointmentCountryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Distinct clku.country_code as country_code,clku.country_name from country_lku clku inner join state_lku slku on clku.country_code=slku.country_code and slku.is_international='1' order by clku.country_name asc

dropdown.name: getAllisAssoicatedAgencyForPublic
dropdown.sqlstmt: select agency_id, IsNull(name,'') + ' (' + cast(agency_id as varchar) + ')' As AssociatedAgencyProducerCode from agency_master where isnull(is_deleted,0)!=1 and isMasterAssociatedAgency=1 order by AssociatedAgencyProducerCode asc

dropdown.name: getDomicileStatesList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select state_id,description from state_lku with(nolock) where country_code='US' order by description asc

dropdown.name: getPaymentTypeForBankInformation
dropdown.sqlstmt: select payment_type_id as payment_type,payment_type_description from payment_type_lku order by payment_type_description

dropdown.name: getResidenceStateList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select state_id as residence_aar_state,description from state_lku where country_code like #residence_country_code# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getResidenceCountryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Distinct clku.country_code as residence_country_code ,clku.country_name,clku.last_updated_by,clku.last_updated_ts from country_lku clku inner join state_lku slku on clku.country_code=slku.country_code and slku.is_international='1' order by clku.country_name asc

dropdown.name: getCountryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Distinct clku.country_code ,clku.country_name,clku.last_updated_by,clku.last_updated_ts from country_lku clku inner join state_lku slku on clku.country_code=slku.country_code and slku.is_international='1' order by clku.country_name asc

dropdown.name: getStateList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select state_id as aar_state,description from state_lku where country_code like #country_code# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getTerritoryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Territory_ID as territory_id,Description as description from Territory_lku order by Description asc

dropdown.name: getBusinessCountryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Distinct clku.country_code as country_code_business,clku.country_name,clku.last_updated_by,clku.last_updated_ts from country_lku clku inner join state_lku slku on clku.country_code=slku.country_code and slku.is_international='1' order by clku.country_name asc

dropdown.name: getBusinessStateListForStep1
dropdown.sqlstmt: select state_id as aar_state_business,description from state_lku where country_code like #country_code_business# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getBusinessCountyListForStep1
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from county_lku where state_id =#aar_state_business# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getMailingCountryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Distinct clku.country_code as country_code_mailing,clku.country_name,clku.last_updated_by,clku.last_updated_ts from country_lku clku inner join state_lku slku on clku.country_code=slku.country_code and slku.is_international='1' order by clku.country_name asc

dropdown.name: getMailingStateListForStep1
dropdown.sqlstmt: select state_id as aar_state_mailing,description from state_lku where country_code like #country_code_mailing# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getMailingCountyListForStep1
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from county_lku where state_id =#aar_state_mailing# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getW9CountryList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select Distinct clku.country_code as country_code_w9,clku.country_name,clku.last_updated_by,clku.last_updated_ts from country_lku clku inner join state_lku slku on clku.country_code=slku.country_code and slku.is_international='1' order by clku.country_name asc

dropdown.name: getW9StateListForStep1
dropdown.sqlstmt: select state_id as aar_state_w9,description from state_lku where country_code like #country_code_w9# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getW9CountyListForStep1
dropdown.sqlstmt: select * from county_lku where state_id =#aar_state_w9# order by description asc

dropdown.name: getContactList
dropdown.sqlstmt: select ta.person_id as person_id,firstname+' '+lastname as contact from tbl_agencyprincipal ta left join tbl_address adr on adr.person_id = ta.person_id where request_id=#aar_requestid# and adr.type=1 order by contact asc
